Printing method for volker lists

print.vlkr_list.Rd

Printing method for volker lists

Usage

# S3 method for class 'vlkr_list'
print(x, ...)

Arguments

x

The volker list.

...

Further parameters passed to print.

Value

No return value.

Examples

library(volker)
data <- volker::chatgpt

rp <- report_metrics(data, sd_age, sd_gender, effect = TRUE)
print(rp)
